media:group.media:title: Let’s Talk - Dad/Daughter Q/A
media:group.media:description: Join Dr. Ken Canfield and Dr. Michelle Watson Canfield as they discuss the importance of the dad/daughter relationship, and how Michelle’s new book, Let’s Talk, Conversation Starters for Dads and Daughters, helps a dad lead his daughter through discussions on key topics—from fun and laughter to deeper issues related to her identity and relationships.
